snippet.title: StageTime - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take the stage with StageTime, the ultimate free-to-play virtual social app launching January 30, 2025, for Meta Quest.

Step into the spotlight and sing karaoke, perform comedy, or share heartfelt poetry in front of a live audience. Customize your avatar, sync videos seamlessly with friends, and join an exciting lineup of events, including the $500 StageTime Showdown, karaoke launch parties, and open mic nights.

Whether you're a seasoned performer or just looking for fun, StageTime is where creativity and connection shine. Get ready to make your mark!

👉 Join the StageTime Discord here: https://discord.gg/stagetime
👉 Download now: https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/stagetime/8938419752938126/
🌐 Check out the website here: https://stagetimevr.com
